Question 4A: Develop and Demonstrate , using javascript script , a XHTML document 
that collects the USN ( the valid format is : A digit followed by two uppercase
characters followed by three digits; no embedded spaces allowed (USN : University 
Seat Number of VTU students :P)) of the user.Event handler must be included for the
form element that collects this information to validate the input. Message in the 
alert window must be produced when errors are detected.

Question 4B: Modify the above program to get the current semester also (restricted 
to be a number from 1 to 8 )
